Describe "N" key press behavior
  it creates a new row for the currently selected collection
  it does nothing if the current collection cannot add more
  
Describe Escape key press
  it ends edits for the currently editing value, not saving changes
  
Describe Any node
  it creates an array if the only non-whitespace character is "["
  it creates an object if the only non-whitespace character is "{"
  it creates a string if the first character is \' or ", not including that first character
  it tries to parse the string as JSON and uses that value if it succeeds
  it can be edited by clicking the closed value, even if it\'s an array or object
  it can be edited like an array node
  